10
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:18,000
Then don't expect
to walk away unscathed either.

11
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,640
Qiao Zhiwei,

12
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,800
we'll pay

13
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,000
for what we've done.

14
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:23,800
What about you?

15
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,800
