16
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:31,320
Then let me tell you

17
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,280
something interesting.

18
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,240
I'm not Qiao Xiaomi.

19
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,880
The girl Dad wanted you to see

20
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:40,720
