something even better.

25
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,320
Want to know who I really am?

26
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,960
I'm the real Qin Yu.

27
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,840
The guy who dated Qiao Xiaomi years ago,

28
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:01,840
his real name was Ji Ran.

29
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:04,200
I lent him my name and my identity.

30
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:07,680
Everything he said is true.

31
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,440
He's the real Qin Yu.

32
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,800
The one who died
in that fire three years ago

33
