85
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,400
Xiaomi.

86
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:16,880
Qiao Xiaomi.

87
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,680
I...

88
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,640
I was wrong.

89
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:19,400
I was wrong.

90
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,400
I don't want anything anymore.

91
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,360
I don't want any of it.

92
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,320
I was wrong.

93
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:28,840
It's all yours.
Take it, take it all.

94
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,760
