276
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:35,640
we're still the two people
who love each other.

277
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:37,720
We're still ourselves.

278
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,080
And we will

279
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,760
find our way back to ourselves.

280
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:48,510
(Qiao Zhiwei faced charges.
Chen Yue faced penalties.)

281
00:16:48,511 --> 00:16:50,120
(Xu Yifei surrendered and assisted.
Qin Yu confessed. No charges filed.)

282
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,920
(Ye Xiaoduo regained her identity.
She resumed life under her real name.)

283
00:17:07,675 --> 00:17:09,745
ظآزWe say good morning, we say good nightظآز

284
00:17:09,745 --> 00:17:13,165
ظآزWe say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurtظآز

285
00:17:14,765 --> 00:17:16,655
ظآزThe sweeter it is, the luckier we seemظآز

286
00:17:16,655 --> 00:17:20,645
ظآزYet the more romantic,
the rougher the roadظآز

287
00:17:21,885 --> 00:17:23,745
ظآزLet me go, set me freeظآز

288
00:17:23,745 --> 00:17:27,785
ظآزLet me drown in reckless silenceظآز

289
00:17:28,325 --> 00:17:33,735
ظآزWe were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted itظآز

290
00:17:35,085 --> 00:17:37,225
ظآزThe freedom you gave meظآز

291
00:17:37,225 --> 00:17:40,865
ظآزBecame the heaviest chain I bearظآز

292
00:17:42,125 --> 00:17:44,395
ظآزLove can barely move forwardظآز

293
00:17:44,395 --> 00:17:48,175
ظآزYet the words still linger unspokenظآز

294
00:17:49,275 --> 00:17:51,515
ظآزThe closeness I long forظآز

295
00:17:51,515 --> 00:17:55,905
ظآزThere's no need for you
to keep avoiding itظآز

296
00:17:56,315 --> 00:17:58,135
ظآزI don't want to break freeظآز

297
00:17:58,135 --> 00:18:03,505
ظآزTake back the chains
disguised as freedomظآز

